divs: Sighting DetailsI stepped out side to gaze at the sky. It was around 9:00pm. The sky was clear. I looked up towards the Northwest, and seen a white sphere shaped object, moving towards the east. It looked as though it was going to go directly over my head, but than abruptly turned South and disappeared.
